ADDITIONAL NOTICES AND DISCLAIMERS

This software is NOT officially supported by FlexRadio Systems, Inc., its 
employees, or its help desk.

This is an independent, community-developed tool created to solve specific 
networking challenges when accessing FlexRadio transceivers over VPN or remote 
connections. While it follows the FlexRadio Discovery Protocol specifications, 
it is not endorsed, maintained, or supported by FlexRadio Systems.

For official FlexRadio support and products, please visit:
  - Website: https://www.flexradio.com
  - Help Desk: https://helpdesk.flexradio.com
  - Community: https://community.flexradio.com

ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This project builds upon the work of the amateur radio community and follows
the VITA-49 standards for radio frequency data transport. Thanks to all 
contributors and the FlexRadio community for their documentation and support.

Original concept inspired by VA3MW's FlexRadio VPN discovery work.
